Line 1 of the file contains metadata, such as the name of the cutscene, and any NPC's present
Subsequent lines contain the script for the cutscene, this is executed line by line, normal text is directly output with no modification, however text within {} will be treated as a variable (useful for getting the player's name, or the name of an NPC from the database)
Other special characters include:
\n for line breaks
standard discord formatting codes such as * for italics, ** for bold, `` for code block's, etc.
